‚ÄúTake two ounces of country, an ounce of Rock and Roll, add a splash of southern hospitality, mix and serve‚Ä¶‚Äù
Our unique blend of unpretentious charm, feel-good music, and mouth watering food has made Renegades a local South Florida legend. Renegades started from humble beginnings and have cemented themselves as a West Palm Beach nightlife favorite. Since our first location on Okeechobee blvd, which opened in 2001, we have grown with our community to our current 9,000 sq ft venue. With continuing enhancements after a change of owners and management in 2017, Renegades continues to develop into the original concept it was meant to be. Complete with Line dancing, Live concerts, 50+ big screen tv‚Äôs and 6 large projectors for those Sunday games. We also have a mechanical bull and so much more than you can imagine. From students to professionals, fun-seekers of all ages can find a reason to enjoy Renegades Country Bar & Grill. Maybe it‚Äôs our enticing menu filled with your favorite burgers, wings, BBQ Ribs, sandwiches and more. Signature Rebel Rolls and Gator Bites are our fan favorites.
Renegades delivers the best live performances by todays local and upcoming artists, plus world-class DJ‚Äôs spinning your favorite country songs and all around fun music! Celebrity guests drop in from time-to-time. Famous acts from Kenny Chesney to Alan Jackson and more have been known to drop in after a shows. So slide on in and take a look around; you never know who you may bump into on the dance floor!

Our Mission Statement
‚ÄúOur mission at Renegades Country Bar is to provide a vibrant and energetic destination where guests can experience the ultimate country music and entertainment experience. We are dedicated to offering a unique blend of country music, line dancing, and Southern-inspired cuisine that celebrates the spirit of the country lifestyle. Our goal is to create a welcoming and inclusive environment where country music enthusiasts of all backgrounds can come together to enjoy great music and friendly camaraderie. We are committed to serving high-quality, flavorful meals inspired by traditional country cooking, using fresh, locally sourced ingredients. We are committed to delivering exceptional service, top-notch entertainment, and a lively atmosphere that keeps our guests coming back for more. At Renegades, we invite you to let loose, kick up your heels, and embrace your inner renegade spirit.
Welcome to the Renegades Country Bar and Grill ‚Äì where good food, good music, and good times come together under one roof.‚Äù
